These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cherry, eggplant, apricot
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, italian, dutch
1. the nigerian is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the person eating apple is the dutch##1
3. the italian is on the right of the mexican##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | eggplant | cherry | apple   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | mexican     | italian   | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, card-games, writing, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, badminton, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | writing | puzzles | card-games | traveling    |
| Sport   | badminton    | cricket      | surfing | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, woodworking, magic-tricks, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, family, superhero, documentary
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | board-games | puzzles | magic-tricks   | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | superhero | documentary | family         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts | musical  | scientific      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rugby   | volleyball | ice-hockey |

