.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, mango, carrot, pumpkin
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, rat, frog
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pumpkin | carrot | mango | watermelon |
| Pet    | bird       | frog | rat | mouse     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, brazilian, indian, colombian
4 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, guinea-pig, turtle
1. the brazilian is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the indian##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | indian | german | brazilian |
| Pet           | horse      | guinea-pig | turtle | lizard    |

