2. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | ambient | funk | blues  |
| Pet           | lizard | guinea-pig | rabbit       | bird |

