.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, software-developer, freelancer, manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, jet-ski, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the software-developer##1
2. the person driving the boat is the manager##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the videographer##1
4. the freelancer is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | freelancer | videographer      | software-developer | manager |
| Transport   | snowmobile          | motorbike | jet-ski     | boat    |

