The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, scooter, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | thriller       | sports | action   |
| Transport     | boat | scooter | van   | bike |

