2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | water | fanta  | soy-milk | tea |
| Transport   | trike | bike | snowmobile          | van    |

