.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, australian, canadian, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, roller, subway, bike
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the australian##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the indonesian is the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | japanese | canadian | australian | indonesian   |
| Transport     | subway  | van    | roller       | bike |

 